        " خَبَرٍ آخَرَ قَالَ قَالَ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنْ كَانَ عِنْدَهُ صَبِيٌّ فَلْيَتَصَابَ لَهُ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4707 - In another narration, the Prophet (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said: \"Whoever has a child should act childishly with him.\""
        ]
